original_title: Mrs. Wiggs of the Cabbage Patch
overview: In the shanty town called the Cabbage Patch, Mrs. Wiggs scrabbles for survival with her brood of children and hopes for the return of her husband, who left many years before.
tagline: AMERICA'S MOST LOVABLE FAMILY COMES TO LIFE ON THE SCREEN!
title: Mrs. Wiggs of the Cabbage Patch
